'''2channel'''（{{jpn|j=2ちゃんねる|rm=ni channeru}}）， 又稱為'''2ch'''<ref name=":3" />、'''Channel 2'''<ref name="OnishiNYT2">{{cite news|last=Ōnishi|first=Norimitsu|date=2004-05-09|title=Japanese Find a Forum to Vent Most-Secret Feelings|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/09/world/japanese-find-a-forum-to-vent-most-secret-feelings.html|access-date=2020-06-04|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202194333/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/09/world/japanese-find-a-forum-to-vent-most-secret-feelings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Q&A With the Founder of Channel 2|url=http://www.ojr.org/japan/internet/1061505583.php|last=Furukawa|first=Hideki|date=2003-08-22|website=Japan Media Review|publisher=USC Annenberg|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031222144247/http://www.ojr.org/japan/internet/1061505583.php|archive-date=2003-12-22|access-date=2020-05-24}}</ref>、'''2ch.net'''<ref name="TokyoDistrictCourt">{{Cite court|litigants= レースクイーン（ＲＱＩ）インク|court=東京地方裁判所|pinpoint=平成29年(ワ)第3428号|url=https://www.courts.go.jp/app/files/hanrei_jp/327/089327_hanrei.pdf|quote=被告は，平成１６年から平成２９年９月３０日まで，継続して本件電子掲示板を管理・運営し }}</ref>，是日本過去的匿名{{link-en|文字討論板|Textboard}}<ref name="KeijibanNote" group="註">日語為{{lang|ja|掲示板}}，其性質跟[[BBS|BBS]]不同，故不能以BBS稱之。</ref>，由[[西村博之|西村博之]]於1999年所創。它是「日本最受欢迎的网络社区，每天用戶數約有1000萬人」<ref name="SakamotoAPJ">{{cite journal|last=Sakamoto|first=Rumi|title='Koreans, Go Home!' Internet Nationalism in Contemporary Japan as a Digitally Mediated Subculture|url=http://www.japanfocus.org/-Rumi-SAKAMOTO/3497|journal=The Asia-Pacific Journal|access-date=2020-05-22|date=2011-03-07|volume=9|issue=10|archive-date=2015-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330083754/http://www.japanfocus.org/-Rumi-SAKAMOTO/3497|dead-url=no}}</ref>，影響力與廣播、電視及報刊等傳統媒體不相上下<ref name="KatayamaWired2007">{{cite news|last=Katayama|first=Lisa|date=2007-04-19|title=2-Channel Gives Japan's Famously Quiet People a Mighty Voice|work=[[连线|Wired]]|url=http://archive.wired.com/culture/lifestyle/news/2007/04/2channel|access-date=2020-05-21|archive-date=2017-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170221051633/http://archive.wired.com/culture/lifestyle/news/2007/04/2channel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2channel在2007年為世上最大型的文字討論板，用戶每天平均建立約250萬個貼文<ref name="KatayamaWired2007"/>，年收入约为1億日元<ref name="KatayamaWired2008">{{cite news|last=Katayama|first=Lisa|date=2008-05-19|title=Meet Hiroyuki Nishimura, the Bad Boy of the Japanese Internet|publisher=Wired|url=https://www.wired.com/techbiz/people/magazine/16-06/mf_hiroyuki?currentPage=2|deadurl=no|access-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527190538/http://www.wired.com/techbiz/people/magazine/16-06/mf_hiroyuki?currentPage=2|archive-date=2008-05-27}}</ref><ref name="ShibuiSG">{{Cite web|title=2channel founder says don't blame him for criminals' posts|url=https://japantoday.com/category/features/kuchikomi/2channel-founder-says-dont-blame-him-for-criminals-posts|last=Shibui|first=Tetsuya|date=2008-08-26|website=Shūkan Gendai|language=en|via=Japan Today|access-date=2020-05-20|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221005842/https://japantoday.com/category/features/kuchikomi/2channel-founder-says-dont-blame-him-for-criminals-posts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

與其他社交媒體相比，2channel及其後繼網站於日本有着較大爭議<ref name=":3"/>——日本[[極右派|極右派]]人士經常在這些網站上出沒（因此又稱為[[網路右翼|網路右翼]]），發表主要是針對[[反韓|韓國]]的[[日本民族問題|仇外]]言論<ref name="SakamotoAPJ"/><ref name="OnishiNYT2"/>。此外輿論亦關注於網站上出現的[[诽谤|诽谤]]言論。截至2008年8月，西村已因网站上的诽谤言論而收到一百多起诉讼<ref name="ShibuiSG"/>。犯罪預告同為輿論的焦點<ref name="AdelsteinDB"/><ref name=":7"/><ref name=":9"/><ref name=":10"/>。[[警視廳|東京警視廳]]於2012年指控2channel默许[[苯丙胺|安非他命]]贩子利用該平台從事不法行為<ref name="JapanTimes20121226"/>，但沒有就此對其進行提告<ref name="AdelsteinDB"/>。

[[旧金山|美國旧金山]]的{{link-en|吉姆·瓦特金斯 (商人)|Jim Watkins (businessman)|吉姆·瓦特金斯}}曾為此一網站提供託管和域名註冊服務<ref name="KatayamaWired2008" /><ref name="MatsutaniJT" /><ref name="McLaughlinWired">{{Cite news|last=McLaughlin|first=Timothy|date=2019-08-06|title=The Weird, Dark History of 8Chan|work=Wired|url=https://www.wired.com/story/the-weird-dark-history-8chan/|access-date=2020-05-21|issn=1059-1028|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828131516/https://www.wired.com/story/the-weird-dark-history-8chan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年，網站的所有權轉交給了Packet Monster公司，但西村仍掌握對網站的控制權<ref name="AdelsteinDB" /><ref name="MartinJT">{{cite news|author=Martin|first=Alex|date=2009-01-24|title=2channel founder ponders next step after forum's sale|work=The Japan Times|url=https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2009/01/24/news/2channel-founder-ponders-next-step-after-forums-sale/|deadurl=yes|access-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023135949/https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2009/01/24/news/2channel-founder-ponders-next-step-after-forums-sale/|archive-date=2020-10-23|quote=Speculation abounds, however, that the move may be a legal trick to deflect further lawsuits filed against Nishimura for the site's frequently libelous content.}}</ref>。2014年2月，瓦特金斯凍結了2ch.net這個域名，致使西村失去2channel的管理資格<ref name="McLaughlinWired" /><ref name="AkimotoJT2014" />。這最終演變成兩個自稱為「合法的2channel」的文字討論板同時存在的情況<ref name="AkimotoJT2014" />——一個為瓦特金斯以Loki Technology公司名義持有的'''5channel'''（{{jpn|j=5ちゃんねる|rm=go channeru}}，域名5ch.net），另一個則為西村以Packet Monster公司名義持有的'''2ch.sc'''{{refn|group=註|name=2chscNameNote|2ch.sc就像以往的2ch.net般，稱自身為{{lang|ja|2ちゃんねる}}。在日語上若要區分兩者，則會在{{lang|ja|2ちゃんねる}}後方加上（2ch.sc）。{{#tag:ref||name=Monolith}}}}<ref name="PacketMonsterCurrent">{{Cite web|script-title=ja:２ちゃんねるガイド：基本|url=http://info.2ch.sc/guide/faq.html|author=西村博之|website=2ch.sc|access-date=2020-05-18|quote=2ch.sc is managed and operated by PACKET MONSTER INC. and more.|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928140838/http://info.2ch.sc/guide/faq.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年9月，2channel用戶每天平均建立超過240萬個貼文<ref name=":15">{{Cite web|date=2007-10-19|title=suzume graph|url=http://pv.40.kg/suzume/|access-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071019001429/http://pv.40.kg/suzume/|archive-date=2007-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref group="註" name="FiguresNote">據官方統計數字。</ref>。截至2020年7月，5channel共有1,031個留言板。週末日平均貼文量約有270万個<ref name="SPARROW5ch">{{cite web|title=SPARROW5ch|url=https://stat.5ch.net/SPARROW/|website=5ch Officially Reported Statistics|access-date=2019-10-25|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130044921/http://stat.5ch.net/SPARROW|dead-url=no}}</ref>——自2016年3月起幾乎沒出現任何成長<ref name="5chStats">{{cite web|title=SPARROW5ch|url=http://stat.5ch.net/SPARROW/20160313/|website=5ch Officially Reported Statistics|access-date=2020-07-17|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914174338/http://stat.5ch.net/SPARROW/20160313/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而2ch.sc則有826個留言板，用戶每日平均建立約5,700個貼文<ref name="2chscStats">{{Cite web|script-title=ja:投稿数統計|url=https://sweet.2ch.sc/posts.html|website=2ch掲示板|access-date=2020-05-16|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914175624/https://sweet.2ch.sc/posts.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
